Data frame of species available

A dataset containing the available species, with SPECIES_CODE, RUN_NAME, SCI_NAME, and PRIMARY_COM_NAME.

runs_w_names

Format

A data frame with 107 rows and 4 variables:

SPECIES_CODE

six letter eBird code in eBird Taxonomy v2016

RUN_NAME

unique analysis identifier and the top level folder name for all results

SCI_NAME

Scientific name from eBird Taxonomy v2016

PRIMARY_COM_NAME

English common name from eBird Taxonomy v2016
